Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰在那附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7、8、9蓄水池破損
