Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷第2、第3 ECS杆損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來把那個粗暴的傢伙\n給我趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒輒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你贏了，凱西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，好像也不是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動SDM，120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告，啟動後無法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您同意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，快點動手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會陪我到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算自我引爆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們來當好朋友吧，凱西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艙門？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧，還剩60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附帶一提，炸藥有300公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,份量足以炸沉這艘船艦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射主動魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射主動魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴薩狄那的主動魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從方位2-9-8接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好誘餌機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快準備再度潛行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高壓空氣尚未充填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離2500
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認魚雷發射管口的開啟聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說想跟你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣…閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除所有攻擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就等於是終於得到了\n期望已久的初次打擊機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽卻因太陽西下而告中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚雷沒來？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跟丟了我方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴薩狄那，在距離1500處停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行艙門正在開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種暴風雨中\n打開飛行艙門根本是自殺行為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann沒有任何異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令是從別處發出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不用擔心，一切都會很順利)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有事的，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣？這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得很難看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你像英雄那般\n帥氣的將我一次擊倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死命掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起華麗又滑稽的走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎，凱西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙你的
