Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認全艦的空氣密閉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以關閉飛行艙門為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，Arbalest(強弩兵)呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼親密地叫我\n 凱西姆、凱西姆的
