Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann，剩下就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，千鳥小姐
