Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，你去跟她說說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鳥
