Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危險吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是釣竿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說那個，這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的釣場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地裡只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要搭往東京的班機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能在這裡\n再待40多分鐘而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我當初的作戰目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是想帶你來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果卻因為各種事而繞了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來，釣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定30分鐘就可以釣到大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就很難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就覺得什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論是釣上超乎想像的大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是從恐怖的危險中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分鐘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的這麼覺得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有你在，我現在才能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就來試試\n你所說的這種好運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拉了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鯛魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是鯨魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不能否定這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要把它釣回家去喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
